{"article_id":"NPA9ybLZwOtnD8k8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The number of people","depth":10},{"id":1,"text":"infected with a new virus in China","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"tripled over the weekend ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"with the outbreak spreading from Wuhan to other major cities .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"There are now more than 200 cases , mostly in Wuhan ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"though the respiratory illness has also been detected in Beijing , Shanghai and Shenzhen .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Three people have died .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Japan , Thailand and South Korea have reported cases .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"The new strain of coronavirus ,","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"which causes a type of pneumonia ,","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"can pass from person to person ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"China confirmed .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Respiratory expert Zhong Nanshan ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"who heads the health commission team","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"investigating the virus ,","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"14 medical workers had caught it","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"while treating patients ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"state media reported .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"The sharp rise comes","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"as millions of Chinese prepare to travel for the Lunar New Year holidays .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Although the outbreak is believed to have originated from a market ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"officials and scientists are yet to determine exactly how it has been spreading .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"The outbreak has revived memories of the Sars virus","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"- also a coronavirus -","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"that killed 774 people in the early 2000s across dozens of countries , mostly in Asia .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"Analysis of the genetic code of the new virus shows","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"it is more closely related to Sars than any other human coronavirus .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Experts in the UK told the BBC","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"the number of people infected could still be far greater","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"than official figures suggest ,","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"with estimates closer to 1,700 .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"2019-nCoV ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"as it 's been labelled ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"is understood to be a new strain of coronavirus","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"that has not previously been identified in humans","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Coronaviruses are a broad family of viruses ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"but only six","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"( the new one would make it seven )","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"are known to infect people","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Scientists believe","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"an animal source is `` the most likely primary source ''","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"but that some human-to-human transmission has occurred","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Signs of infection include respiratory symptoms , fever , cough , shortness of breath and breathing difficulties","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"People are being advised to avoid `` unprotected '' contact with live animals ,","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"thoroughly cook meat and eggs ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"and avoid close contact with anyone with cold or flu-like symptoms","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Authorities in Wuhan , a central Chinese city of 11 million","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that has been at the heart of the outbreak ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"on Monday said","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"136 new cases had been confirmed over the weekend ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"with a third person dying of the virus .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"There had previously been only 62 confirmed cases in the city .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"As of late Sunday , officials said","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"170 people in Wuhan were still being treated in hospital ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"including nine in critical condition .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Beijing also confirmed its first cases , with five people infected .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Shanghai confirmed its first case on Monday","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"- a 56-year-old woman","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"who came from Wuhan .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"In the city of Shenzhen , a major tech hub close to Hong Kong , officials said","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"a 66-year-old man showed symptoms of the virus","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"following a trip","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"to visit relatives in Wuhan .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Four cases have been confirmed abroad","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"- two in Thailand , one in Japan and one in South Korea -","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"all of them involving people","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"who are either from Wuhan","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"or have visited the city .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"In South Korea , the Korea Centers for Disease Control and Prevention said","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"a 35-year-old Chinese woman was suffering from a fever and respiratory problems","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"after travelling there from Wuhan .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"She was put into isolation","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"and treated at a local hospital .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"The World Health Organization said","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"it was currently not recommending restrictions on travel or trade ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"but was providing guidance to countries","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"preparing for any outbreak .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Airports in Singapore , Hong Kong and the Japanese capital Tokyo have been screening air passengers from Wuhan ,","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"and US authorities last week announced similar measures at three major airports in San Francisco , Los Angeles and New York .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"How China is responding to the outbreak is under close scrutiny ,","depth":4},{"id":81,"text":"given that it was widely criticised","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"for initially covering up the Sars crisis in late 2002 and early 2003 .","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"On Monday , Chinese President Xi Jinping for the first time publicly addressed the outbreak ,","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"that the virus must be `` resolutely contained '' .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"The foreign ministry , meanwhile , said","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"China was providing `` timely information about the disease ''","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"and would `` work with all parties","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"to deal with the virus '' .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"China 's National Health Commission on Monday confirmed","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that two cases in China were due to human-to-human transmission ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"state-run Xinhua news agency reported .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"The commission had earlier said","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"there had been no such cases ,","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"but that the virus had instead crossed the species barrier","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"and come from infected animals at a seafood and wildlife market in Wuhan .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"The WHO also said","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"it believed","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"there had been `` some limited human-to-human transmission","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"occurring between close contacts '' .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"`` As more... cases are identified","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"and more analysis undertaken ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"we will get a clearer picture of disease severity and transmission patterns , ''","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"it wrote on Twitter .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"It noted","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"that the rise in cases in China was a result of `` increased searching and testing for [ the virus ] among people sick with respiratory illness '' .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"From Friday , most Chinese will begin their week-long Lunar New Year holidays .","depth":4},{"id":108,"text":"It 's a time","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"when hundreds of millions travel around China","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"to visit family ,","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"raising fears","depth":4},{"id":112,"text":"that authorities will not be able to adequately monitor further spread of the disease .","depth":4},{"id":113,"text":"Wuhan is a transport hub","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"and authorities there have for nearly a week been using temperature scanners at airports , and train and bus stations .","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"Those","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"showing signs of fever","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"have been registered ,","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"given masks","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"and taken to hospitals and clinics .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"Authorities say","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"they will now also be screening everyone","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"leaving the city .","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"At Beijing 's central railway station , some travellers donned masks","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"but did not appear overly concerned about the virus .","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"`` Watching the news ,","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"I do feel a little worried .","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"But I have n't taken precautionary measures","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"beyond wearing regular masks , ''","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"Li Yang , a 28-year-old account manager","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"travelling to the region of Inner Mongolia ,","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"told the AFP news agency .","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"But the tone in Chinese social media ,","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"where the outbreak has been a top trending topic ,","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"was different .","depth":5},{"id":135,"text":"`` Who knows","depth":6},{"id":136,"text":"how many people","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"who have been to Wuhan","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"may be unaware","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"that they have already been infected ? ''","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"one Weibo user said .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":281,"left":247,"right":280,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":247,"left":220,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":187,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":183,"right":186,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":183,"left":161,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":148,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":144,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":143,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":142,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":142,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":145,"right":146,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":146,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":160,"left":158,"right":159,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":151,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":150,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":149,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":154,"right":156,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":15,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":12,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":13,"right"